<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Frequently Asked Questions</title>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Smooch+Sans:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/navbar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/faqs.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('./navbar') %>
        <div class="container-faq" id="faq">
            <h2 class="faq-heading">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="accordion">
                <div class="faq">
                    <div class="faq__question">
                        What is anxiety?
                        <button class="faq__button font-bold"><span class="text-3xl">+</span></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq__answer-0 hidden">Anxiety is a normal emotion that everyone experiences.
                        However, an
                        anxiety disorder involves excessive, persistent worry or fear that can interfere with daily
                        life.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq">
                    <div class="faq__question">
                        What is depression?
                        <button class="faq__button font-bold"><span class="text-3xl">+</span></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq__answer-1 hidden">Depression is a mood disorder characterized by persistent feelings
                        of
                        sadness, loss of interest or pleasure in activities, and other symptoms that can impact daily
                        functioning.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq">
                    <div class="faq__question">
                        What is self-care in relation to mental health?
                        <button class="faq__button font-bold"><span class="text-3xl">+</span></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq__answer-2 hidden">Self-care involves taking deliberate actions to maintain and
                        improve
                        one's physical, emotional, and mental well-being. It can include activities like exercise,
                        relaxation techniques, and spending time on hobbies

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq">
                    <div class="faq__question">
                        What is therapy or counseling?
                        <button class="faq__button font-bold"><span class="text-3xl">+</span></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq__answer-3 hidden">Therapy or counseling is a process where individuals talk to a
                        trained
                        mental health professional about their thoughts, feelings, and behaviors. It aims to help them
                        understand and manage their emotions better.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Add more FAQ items as needed -->
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="/javascripts/faqs.js"></script>
</body>

</html>